titles.title: Providing for the printing of the book entitled "Members of the United States House of Representatives: A Historical Bibliography".

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on House Administration.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Personnel and Police.
Subcommittee Consideration and Mark-up Session Held.
Forwarded by Subcommittee to Full Committee by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 9/27/1994--Introduced. Provides for the printing as a House document of the book entitled "Members of the United States House of Representatives: A Historical Bibliography," prepared by the Office of the Historian of the House of Representatives.
